Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.24,0:24:14.84,ED CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}但也没有动摇到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.84,0:24:17.68,ED CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}仅此唯一属于我们两人的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.20,0:24:21.12,ED CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}即便明天会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.72,0:24:24.92,ED CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}但你却依然不变
